{"tid":1002667,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歧視香港人] 西營盤酒樓優先請新移民","createTime":"2019-01-31T06:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T11:01:20.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a31fd9419a3abe1879f080b8783109753c63af62","tid":1002667,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:20:48.000Z","msg":"中港融合，理應香港人內地人一家親，任何行業請人都唔應該涉及歧視某類人、又或者優待某類人。之但係有網民發現，西營盤第二街一間即將開業嘅「潮州風X酒家」，仲有西環太平洋廣場已開業嘅「津X大飯店」，招聘廣告上都寫明「新移民及講普通話者優先錄用」，被指係歧視香港人之舉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/iZCVHpzq1roc0oB.bvwU.g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODExO2g9ODMx/https://media.zenfs.com/en/heawork.tumblr.com/14324454c322871245840275f0eae14d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FiZCVHpzq1roc0oB.bvwU.g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODExO2g9ODMx%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fheawork.tumblr.com%2F14324454c322871245840275f0eae14d&h=dee6cf9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔少網民見到呢兩個招聘廣告都好嬲，仲揚言話要報平機會，可惜根據目前法例，平機會都未必受理，因為根本無「香港人歧視」呢個條目。<br />\n所以網民就即刻轉口風，話要發揮消費者力量，永不幫襯咁話！ <br />\n唔止酒樓，其實依家好多連鎖零售店、超市、食肆都請多咗好多普通話非常流利嘅人，再舉目四周望吓自己個辦公室，請ABC已經過時，識請緊係請「Zhi Chi Shi」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DF7sPAsQTAImub6r5jc2nA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/heawork.tumblr.com/d1b54530828f5062b39ca1d1f244a8da\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDF7sPAsQTAImub6r5jc2nA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fheawork.tumblr.com%2Fd1b54530828f5062b39ca1d1f244a8da&h=74fc9659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小編覺得，大愛啲講，講咩語言，都可以係好同事（你睇啲外國人，同班女同事一齊食飯幾開心），都可以對社會有貢獻，但如果愈來愈多好似「潮州風X酒家」呢類空缺咁，香港人會有咩後果，真係難以預料了。"},{"pid":"1fed85e43e97dbc6581f69677548f7c5668b4f46","tid":1002667,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:56:50.000Z","msg":"罷食啦<br />\n雖然不嬲冇人食<br />\n垃圾酒樓"},{"pid":"ebc05122d65367fac470571ca9cb6abcff419589","tid":1002667,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"請香港人啦<br />\n香港人會OT架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}